findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions mintNFT(), reserveVIP(), Giveaways() uses a loop to mint tokens and may cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a large number of numTokens.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to modify critical parameters and perform sensitive operations.
